# Chapter Overview

Window Functions are among the most powerful features in SQL.

Unlike aggregate functions,

window functions allow us to perform calculations across multiple rows

**without reducing the number of rows returned.**

This capability makes them indispensable for

- Data Engineering
- Business Intelligence
- Financial Analytics
- Reporting
- Data Warehousing
- Time Series Analysis
- Machine Learning Feature Engineering

Nearly every senior SQL interview contains questions involving window functions.

Understanding them thoroughly is one of the biggest milestones in becoming an advanced SQL developer.

