# The Fundamental Rule

`PARTITION BY`

divides one large window

into

multiple smaller windows.

Each partition is processed

independently.

Think of it as

```
Entire Table

↓

Split Into Windows

↓

Window Function

↓

Merge Results
```

Notice

Rows are **never removed.**

