# NULL Handling

The same NULL rules apply.

```
COUNT(*)

↓

Counts Rows

-------------------

COUNT(column)

↓

Ignores NULL

-------------------

COUNT(DISTINCT)

↓

Ignores NULL
```

Only

`COUNT(*)`

counts every row.

