# Best Practices

✅ Use `DENSE_RANK()` when ties should share the same rank.

✅ Choose it when rank numbers must remain consecutive.

✅ Use `PARTITION BY` for department-wise or region-wise rankings.

✅ Add a separate final `ORDER BY` if deterministic display order is required.

