```

Expected Result

| Date | Sales | Previous Day |
|------|------:|-------------:|
|1 Jan|100|NULL|
|2 Jan|120|100|
|3 Jan|150|120|
|4 Jan|130|150|

This is impossible

using

GROUP BY.

It is simple

using

```
LAG()
```

---

