↓

Yesterday's Sales

↓

Running Total
```

Query

```sql
SELECT

sale_date,

sales,

LAG(sales)

OVER
(
ORDER BY sale_date
)

AS previous_sales,

SUM(sales)

OVER
(
ORDER BY sale_date
)

AS running_total

FROM daily_sales;
```

---

Result

| Date | Sales | Previous | Running Total |
|------|------:|---------:|--------------:|
|1 Jan|100|NULL|100|
|2 Jan|120|100|220|
|3 Jan|150|120|370|
|4 Jan|130|150|500|

