# Chapter Overview

Congratulations!

You have completed one of the most important chapters in PostgreSQL.

In this chapter,

you learned how window functions allow SQL to perform powerful analytical calculations while preserving every row in the result set.

Unlike

```
GROUP BY
```

window functions

do not collapse rows.

Instead,

they calculate results

over a logical window

of related rows.

---

