# Aggregate Window Functions

Purpose

```
Calculate

Values

Across

Rows
```

Functions

| Function | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| SUM() | Running totals, totals |
| AVG() | Running average, group average |
| COUNT() | Row counts |
| MIN() | Minimum value |
| MAX() | Maximum value |

Common Use Cases

- Running totals
- Department averages
- Customer counts
- Sales summaries

---

# Ranking Functions

Purpose

```
Assign

Positions

To Rows
```

Functions

| Function | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| ROW_NUMBER() | Unique numbering |
| RANK() | Shared rank with gaps |
| DENSE_RANK() | Shared rank without gaps |
| NTILE() | Equal-sized groups |

---

# Navigation Functions

Purpose

```
Access

Other Rows
```

Functions

| Function | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| LAG() | Previous row |
| LEAD() | Next row |
| FIRST_VALUE() | First row value |
| LAST_VALUE() | Last row value |
| NTH_VALUE() | Nth row value |

---

# Window Clause Anatomy

Every window function

uses

```
OVER()
```

Possible components

```sql
OVER
(
PARTITION BY ...

ORDER BY ...

ROWS ...
)
```

Remember

```
PARTITION BY

↓

Creates Groups

------------------------

ORDER BY

↓

Defines Sequence

------------------------

ROWS / RANGE / GROUPS

↓

Defines Window Frame
```

