# Final Words

Window functions

are one of the most valuable SQL features for analytics.

They allow you to answer complex business questions using concise, expressive SQL while preserving row-level detail.

Mastering them will improve your ability to write reporting queries, build dashboards, design ETL pipelines, and solve advanced interview problems.

